== 评价 ==
Substream杂志对《Bad Frequencies》给予了积极的评价，认为霍桑高地在连续五年未发行新录音室专辑的情况下，仍然很好地把握住了乐队的进步及反思之间的平衡<ref>{{Cite web|title=REVIEW: Hawthorne Heights Mix Past And Present On "Bad Frequencies"|url=https://substreammagazine.com/2018/04/review-hawthorne-heights-bad-frequencies/|accessdate=2021-03-21|author=Logan White|date=2018-04-23|publisher=Substream Magazine|language=英语|archive-date=2019-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825055616/https://substreammagazine.com/2018/04/review-hawthorne-heights-bad-frequencies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与此同时，Allmusic及Cryptic Rock的评论均认为虽然专辑的整体质量较高，但创作框架及路线缺乏可圈可点之处，较于霍桑高地此前的作品没有明显的突破<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bad Frequencies - Hawthorne Heights|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/bad-frequencies-mw0003159622|accessdate=2021-03-21|publisher=AllMusic|language=英语|archive-date=2019-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825055612/https://www.allmusic.com/album/bad-frequencies-mw0003159622|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=HAWTHORNE HEIGHTS – BAD FREQUENCIES (ALBUM REVIEW)|url=https://crypticrock.com/hawthorne-heights-bad-frequencies-album-review/|accessdate=2021-03-21|author=Jeannie Blue|date=2018-04-23|publisher=Cryptic Rock|language=英语|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033241/https://crypticrock.com/hawthorne-heights-bad-frequencies-album-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

